content: That's really helpful information about obtaining a clear title deed. I actually inherited a piece of land from my great aunt who passed away last year, and I finally received the title deed in the mail on January 25th. I'm not sure what I want to do with it yet, but I'm considering selling it or using it for a small farm or orchard project. Do you have any advice on how to determine the value of the land and what factors to consider when making a decision?
